title: “I wasn’t convicted of a crime”: Tectone breaks silence after sexual assault court case details surface online
summary_full: Streamer Tectone addressed viral claims about a sexual assault-related court case, denying any criminal conviction or jail risk and stating the matter was a civil hearing. Fellow streamer Mizkif disputed his account, alleging serious findings, restraining orders, and NDAs involving Tectone’s ex-partners. Tectone has not responded to Mizkif’s latest statements, leaving the controversy unresolved.
